high_descs: Turn to the right, then to the right again to face the end of the island counter.
Pick up the brown bowl from the counter top.
Turn to the right and go straight to face the refrigerator.
Place the bowl in the refrigerator, wait a few seconds, and remove the bowl from the refrigerator.
Turn around, go straight, then left to face the counter top to the left of the sink.
Place the bowl in the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the chilled bowl in the left sink.

high_descs: Walk forward around the center table and turn right to face the center table.
Pick up the bowl on the center table.
Turn right and walk forward to face the fridge.
Cool the bowl in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn left and walk forward to face the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To cool a bowl plus place it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn and go to the center counter.
Pick up a bowl on the center counter.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the bowl in the refrigerator.
Turn and go to the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl in the sink.
